window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When the dice are loaded, the claws come out.</p> <p>Rudy and Thomas have landed in Sin City, but not on all four paws. The Talking Animal Union is determined to trip up the Freelance Familiars and entangle Thomas in a game where Death holds all the cards.</p> <p>But Thomas canâ€™t focus merely on saving himself. A vampire stalks the refugees of Grantsville, and to save his friends - and his own neck - Thomas has to put more than just himself on the line.</p> <p>The odds are raw and bloody in Vegas....</p>"; 
